WEBVTT

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:04.750
SERN will take your time machine now.

00:00:04.750 --> 00:00:07.290
SERN?! What do you mean?!

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.870
Makise Kurisu...

00:00:09.870 --> 00:00:11.290
Okabe Rintaro...

00:00:11.290 --> 00:00:13.000
Hashida Itaru...

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.410
You three will come with us.

00:00:17.330 --> 00:00:20.660
Wh-What about Mayuri...?

00:00:20.660 --> 00:00:23.080
Shiina Mayuri...

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.370
...is unnecessary.

00:00:29.660 --> 00:00:31.580
Stop...

00:00:33.330 --> 00:00:35.620
Please stop...!

00:00:35.620 --> 00:00:37.500
For FB...

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:40.290
FB... FB...!

00:01:02.950 --> 00:01:04.750
Mayuri...

00:01:04.750 --> 00:01:06.450
Mayuri!

00:01:09.870 --> 00:01:11.700
Mayuri...

00:01:17.580 --> 00:01:20.040
What is this?!

00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:29.000
Get away from her.

00:01:31.450 --> 00:01:32.830
Okabe!

00:01:32.830 --> 00:01:36.250
Get away! Before she kills you too!

00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:41.000
I'll get you for this...

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:44.080
She was my...!

00:02:12.790 --> 00:02:17.200
The 42 inch CRT...

00:02:18.290 --> 00:02:19.950
It's on now.

00:02:25.450 --> 00:02:27.120
Hurry!

00:02:35.910 --> 00:02:36.870
Okabe!

00:02:36.870 --> 00:02:38.040
I'll go!

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:40.580
But if this doesn't work...!

00:02:40.580 --> 00:02:42.410
Just hurry!

00:02:45.660 --> 00:02:47.540
Okabe!

00:02:49.330 --> 00:02:53.160
Leap!

00:03:11.290 --> 00:03:16.500
For you, billions and billions of heartbeats

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:23.160
are nothing at all; just the blink of an eye

00:03:23.160 --> 00:03:28.370
Although I'm trapped by
the past and lament the future

00:03:28.370 --> 00:03:34.290
inevitability won't allow for
even a speck of a miscalculation

00:03:34.290 --> 00:03:40.410
Our dreams and futures that
form and expand into "infinity"

00:03:40.410 --> 00:03:46.250
allow us the right to be vain,

00:03:46.250 --> 00:03:52.500
while the two hands
point out what is "finite"

00:03:52.500 --> 00:03:57.080
All of which leads to a cruel
contract and choice to make

00:03:57.080 --> 00:03:59.330
Hacking to the Gate

00:03:59.330 --> 00:04:06.250
So, now, with each passing
second, I'll cross world lines

00:04:06.250 --> 00:04:11.160
to protect that smile on your face

00:04:11.160 --> 00:04:18.160
Then, once again, into a
time loop without sadness

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:24.830
I will be swallowed up as a lone observer

00:04:33.450 --> 00:04:40.450
Mayuri's grandmother died when
Mayuri was still in grade school.

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:45.540
Mayuri would visit her grave

00:04:45.540 --> 00:04:50.540
every day for the next six months.

00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:55.040
With her grandmother's
pocket watch in hand,

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:58.700
she would always,
always, gaze up at the sky.

00:04:59.580 --> 00:05:04.500
Almost as if she was waiting for
her grandmother to come get her.

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:09.910
Then, one day, there was a light.

00:05:16.250 --> 00:05:18.450
Crepuscular rays...

00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:22.000
Sometimes known as an "Angel's Ladder."

00:05:22.870 --> 00:05:26.080
It almost seemed like it was
about to take Mayuri away.

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:32.700
It seemed like she was
about to vanish forever...

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:34.330
Mayuri!

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:40.410
Okarin?

00:05:40.410 --> 00:05:42.540
I won't let you get taken away.

00:05:42.540 --> 00:05:44.830
You're my hostage.

00:05:44.830 --> 00:05:47.950
You're my living sacrifice
for my human experiments.

00:05:47.950 --> 00:05:53.330
What came out of my mouth
was a line I picked up as a kid.

00:05:54.370 --> 00:06:00.910
A line a mad scientist inanely shouted
on a TV show we'd seen together.

00:06:02.330 --> 00:06:03.950
Oh.

00:06:05.700 --> 00:06:12.450
So Mayushii is Okarin's hostage?

00:06:12.450 --> 00:06:15.910
Then I guess that's just how it is...

00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:35.450
What's with you?

00:06:35.450 --> 00:06:38.040
Did you doze off or something?

00:06:48.870 --> 00:06:51.250
-What time is it?!
-Huh?

00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:53.500
-What time is it?!
-What's your problem?

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:55.370
It's almost 5:00.

00:06:55.370 --> 00:06:57.790
We're going shopping, remember?

00:06:57.790 --> 00:06:59.700
Shopping?

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:02.250
Okay, I'll order some pizzas then!

00:07:02.250 --> 00:07:05.290
Thanks! Just no Hawaiian pizzas, please.

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:08.330
-I can't stomach them.
-Agreed.

00:07:08.330 --> 00:07:12.160
The time leap worked...?

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:13.080
Okabe.

00:07:13.080 --> 00:07:14.080
Mayuri!

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.250
Where's Mayuri?!

00:07:15.250 --> 00:07:17.660
What brought that on?

00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:24.290
Mayushii just left, remember?
She went to invite Miss Ruka to the party.

00:07:24.290 --> 00:07:25.750
Are you going shopping?

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:28.410
The development conference is canceled!

00:07:28.410 --> 00:07:30.000
Canceled? Why?

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.410
Did something happen?

00:07:31.410 --> 00:07:36.450
We're done for today!
Both of you, go home immediately!

00:07:36.450 --> 00:07:38.450
-What are you talking about?
-Just go!

00:07:38.450 --> 00:07:40.370
Got it?! Just do as I say!

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:43.290
What's his deal?

00:07:43.290 --> 00:07:47.540
His phone rang, and then suddenly he's all...

00:07:47.540 --> 00:07:49.250
His phone?

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:55.120
Too-too-roo! This is Mayushii!

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:57.700
I can't come to the phone right now.

00:07:57.700 --> 00:07:59.540
Please leave your message--

00:08:03.040 --> 00:08:08.540
The world line hasn't changed much,
unlike whenever we send D-mails.

00:08:08.540 --> 00:08:11.620
I've really gone back to 5:00 pm today...

00:08:12.620 --> 00:08:14.330
Clackety-clack!

00:08:14.330 --> 00:08:16.700
Bullet train!

00:08:16.700 --> 00:08:20.160
No, honey, bullet trains are white.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:25.450
After this, Mayuri brings
Suzuha to the lab and...

00:08:27.330 --> 00:08:29.370
Should I go to the police?!

00:08:29.370 --> 00:08:34.250
No, no one would believe that
I've time-leapt from the future!

00:08:34.910 --> 00:08:37.790
I have to do something
within the next three hours!

00:08:38.370 --> 00:08:39.040
"Yanabayashi Shrine"

00:08:39.040 --> 00:08:41.450
Mayuri! Mayuri!

00:08:41.450 --> 00:08:42.870
O-Okab--

00:08:42.870 --> 00:08:44.500
I mean, Kyouma--

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.450
Where's Mayuri?!

00:08:46.450 --> 00:08:49.660
-She already left...
-She left?! When?!

00:08:49.660 --> 00:08:52.790
A-About half an hour ago.

00:08:52.790 --> 00:08:55.080
She said she was heading back to the lab.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:57.370
Is she not back yet?

00:08:57.370 --> 00:08:59.040
Umm, I'm sorry.

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:03.660
It was very nice of you to invite
me to your party, but today I have to--

00:09:03.660 --> 00:09:05.750
Any mention of stopping by somewhere first?!

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:08.540
You mean Mayuri-chan? No...

00:09:08.540 --> 00:09:12.120
If you see her, have her call me right away!

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:14.700
O-Okay.

00:09:14.700 --> 00:09:17.910
If the world line hasn't changed,

00:09:17.910 --> 00:09:22.500
then neither will Mayuri's actions--
unless I can change them somehow!

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:25.410
Where is she?!

00:09:25.410 --> 00:09:26.660
Meow, meow!

00:09:26.660 --> 00:09:29.250
Faris can't come to the
phone right now, meow!

00:09:29.250 --> 00:09:30.830
Please leave your message at the--

00:09:37.620 --> 00:09:39.790
Where are you, Mayuri?

00:09:40.700 --> 00:09:41.700
Mayuri?!

00:09:41.700 --> 00:09:43.620
Sorry to disappoint.

00:09:43.620 --> 00:09:45.450
It's you, Assistant...

00:09:45.450 --> 00:09:47.870
I told you we're done for today. Leave at--

00:09:47.870 --> 00:09:49.330
Just answer me this.

00:09:49.330 --> 00:09:53.080
You time-leapt from the future, didn't you?

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:58.000
How did you know?

00:09:58.000 --> 00:10:02.250
It was like you completely changed
the instant you answered your phone.

00:10:02.250 --> 00:10:05.290
Given your behavior,
I take it something's happened?

00:10:05.290 --> 00:10:09.750
Yeah. But I don't have time to explain now.

00:10:09.750 --> 00:10:11.000
Just run.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.830
Where to, though?

00:10:12.830 --> 00:10:16.120
Anywhere. Just as far
from the lab as possible!

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:17.700
Got it?

00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:21.000
-You better explain later.
-I will.

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.450
Tell Daru, too.

00:10:22.450 --> 00:10:24.080
All right.

00:10:24.080 --> 00:10:25.160
Okabe.

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:26.750
Yeah?

00:10:26.750 --> 00:10:29.370
Don't do anything crazy, okay?

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:32.660
I know.

00:10:35.500 --> 00:10:37.410
Okabe Rintaro!

00:10:37.410 --> 00:10:41.040
-Hey, which way is Ochanomizu--
-Have you seen Mayuri?!

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.080
Shiina Mayuri?

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:45.580
Yeah, she just invited me to your party--

00:10:45.580 --> 00:10:49.250
-Where?!
-Turn right at that corner--

00:10:49.250 --> 00:10:51.620
Hey! Which way is Ochanomizu?!

00:10:51.620 --> 00:10:54.660
I'm supposed to take
Nae there to go shopping!

00:10:54.660 --> 00:10:56.500
Just ask a policeman!

00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:59.200
Also, when you take her
there, do not come back!

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.700
Why not?!

00:11:00.700 --> 00:11:02.330
I'll explain later!

00:11:17.950 --> 00:11:19.580
Mayuri...

00:11:19.580 --> 00:11:20.580
Mayuri!

00:11:20.580 --> 00:11:22.450
Oh, Okarin!

00:11:22.450 --> 00:11:25.250
Look! The first star of the night!

00:11:25.250 --> 00:11:28.200
-Wh-What's going on?!
-Just come with me!

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:30.120
Huh? What about the party?

00:11:30.120 --> 00:11:31.500
It's canceled!

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:33.200
I've already told Kurisu and Daru!

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.750
Huh? How come?

00:11:34.750 --> 00:11:36.370
I'll explain later!

00:11:36.370 --> 00:11:40.500
But I already invited Suzu-san,
and Daru-kun ordered pizza--

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:43.580
Just do what I say!

00:11:43.580 --> 00:11:45.410
Okarin...

00:11:46.410 --> 00:11:49.870
Sorry.

00:11:49.870 --> 00:11:53.950
Mayushii doesn't understand...

00:11:53.950 --> 00:11:57.580
You always do things
she doesn't understand,

00:11:57.580 --> 00:12:01.660
but today you're really hard to understand.

00:12:01.660 --> 00:12:05.540
I guess... you wanted to
do the experiment after all...

00:12:05.540 --> 00:12:07.330
Mayuri...

00:12:10.830 --> 00:12:12.910
That's not true.

00:12:12.910 --> 00:12:16.410
But, please, listen to me for now.

00:12:17.580 --> 00:12:19.870
There's no time.

00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:23.160
I promise I'll explain later.

00:12:23.160 --> 00:12:24.540
Okay.

00:12:24.540 --> 00:12:28.370
Sorry. Mayushii was just really shocked...

00:12:28.370 --> 00:12:32.540
Don't apologize.
You haven't done anything wrong.

00:12:40.080 --> 00:12:42.080
Look at all these people...

00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:44.750
Yeah, it's rush hour.

00:12:45.370 --> 00:12:49.250
Oh? But the platforms are empty...

00:12:50.500 --> 00:12:56.410
Again, a bomb threat has shut down
all trains on the following lines...

00:12:56.410 --> 00:12:58.870
They still don't know when
the trains'll be running again.

00:12:58.870 --> 00:13:01.200
-Urgh! What a pain!
-How could I be so careless...

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.500
...at a time like this?!

00:13:02.500 --> 00:13:04.160
-Okarin?
-Mayuri!

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:06.540
The subway! Hurry--!

00:13:06.540 --> 00:13:09.120
Okabe Rintaro, I presume?

00:13:12.580 --> 00:13:14.200
What's wrong?

00:13:17.700 --> 00:13:19.660
You're coming with us.

00:13:19.660 --> 00:13:23.450
Hey! Don't block the way! Move!

00:13:23.450 --> 00:13:25.080
Run!

00:13:31.700 --> 00:13:32.700
Run!

00:13:32.700 --> 00:13:34.450
As fast as you can!

00:13:36.540 --> 00:13:39.580
Who are they?!

00:13:39.580 --> 00:13:40.450
Okarin!

00:13:40.450 --> 00:13:41.830
Get out of here!

00:13:41.830 --> 00:13:43.750
Run, Mayuri!

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:06.620
The deceased is Shiina Mayuri.

00:14:06.620 --> 00:14:11.080
Okabe-kun- I mean,
Okabe Rintaro has been secured.

00:14:11.080 --> 00:14:13.370
Mayuri!

00:14:13.370 --> 00:14:16.080
Damn you!

00:14:16.080 --> 00:14:17.160
I won't let you kill her!

00:14:17.160 --> 00:14:20.250
I will save you, Mayuri!

00:14:23.410 --> 00:14:25.040
I will!

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:30.750
I swear it!

00:14:37.700 --> 00:14:39.620
Canceled? Why?

00:14:39.620 --> 00:14:42.160
Did something happen?

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:44.910
Yes. You see...

00:14:44.910 --> 00:14:48.660
I have intel that Mr. Braun will
be storming the place tonight.

00:14:48.660 --> 00:14:51.790
Okarin. Did you get into trouble again?

00:14:51.790 --> 00:14:54.080
Yes. You know how it is.

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:56.910
-But what about Mayuri?
-I'll tell her myself.

00:14:56.910 --> 00:14:59.580
In any case, it's dangerous to stay here.

00:14:59.580 --> 00:15:01.450
You're dismissed for today!

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:06.580
Was that too forceful?

00:15:06.580 --> 00:15:10.620
No... I don't care if
I seem suspicious or not.

00:15:10.620 --> 00:15:14.790
What matters most is getting
everyone away from the lab!

00:15:14.790 --> 00:15:18.080
Too-too-roo! This is Mayushii!

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:20.620
I can't come to the phone right now.

00:15:24.450 --> 00:15:26.620
This keeps taking me too long!

00:15:26.620 --> 00:15:28.790
It's going to be just like last time!

00:15:28.790 --> 00:15:30.620
I have to find Mayuri somehow...!

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.580
"Calling Rukako"

00:15:37.290 --> 00:15:38.580
-Hello?
-Rukako!

00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:40.080
It's me! Okabe!

00:15:40.080 --> 00:15:42.540
Oh, Okabe-- I'm sorry.
I mean Kyouma-san!

00:15:42.540 --> 00:15:43.580
-Mayuri!
-Huh?

00:15:43.580 --> 00:15:44.660
Is Mayuri there?!

00:15:44.660 --> 00:15:46.620
Oh, Mayuri-chan?

00:15:46.620 --> 00:15:49.700
-Yes, she's leaving--
-Stop her!

00:15:49.700 --> 00:15:53.330
Tell her to absolutely
stay put until I get there!

00:15:53.330 --> 00:15:57.000
-But she's going to the lab--
-Just do it!

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:58.330
R-Right!

00:15:58.330 --> 00:16:00.080
Mayuri-chan!

00:16:01.790 --> 00:16:03.830
Clackety-clack!

00:16:03.830 --> 00:16:05.830
Bullet train!

00:16:05.830 --> 00:16:09.660
No, honey, bullet trains are white.

00:16:11.160 --> 00:16:12.750
Mayuri!

00:16:12.750 --> 00:16:16.250
Oh, Okarin! Too-too-roo!

00:16:18.540 --> 00:16:20.120
Are you okay?

00:16:20.120 --> 00:16:24.250
I was just about to fix Fubuki-chan's
costume and head back to the lab...

00:16:24.250 --> 00:16:27.000
Fubuki-chan? A cosplayer friend of yours?

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:32.620
Yeah! She just texted about some loose
threads in the costume Mayushii made--

00:16:32.620 --> 00:16:34.910
So that's where she was?

00:16:34.910 --> 00:16:38.870
I'll go straight to the lab when I'm done!
I'll make it in time for the party!

00:16:38.870 --> 00:16:40.950
Wait! The party is...

00:16:40.950 --> 00:16:43.950
The party is cancel--

00:16:43.950 --> 00:16:46.910
-...It's been postponed.
-Huh?! How come?!

00:16:46.910 --> 00:16:50.120
We can't use the lab, you see...

00:16:50.120 --> 00:16:52.080
It's out of our hands.

00:16:52.080 --> 00:16:53.500
Oh...

00:16:53.500 --> 00:16:57.540
Anyway, I need you
to come with me, Mayuri.

00:16:57.540 --> 00:16:59.000
Right now.

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.790
-What about Fubuki-chan?
-Sorry, but she'll have to wait.

00:17:01.790 --> 00:17:03.080
This is extremely important.

00:17:03.080 --> 00:17:05.580
Umm, did something happen?

00:17:05.580 --> 00:17:09.250
Yeah. We're going on a little outing now.

00:17:09.250 --> 00:17:10.580
-A trip.
-Huh?!

00:17:10.580 --> 00:17:13.040
Th-Th-The two of you are?!

00:17:13.040 --> 00:17:14.870
Oh, I mean...

00:17:16.080 --> 00:17:19.950
I can always go see Fubuki-chan
tomorrow, but this is so sudden...

00:17:19.950 --> 00:17:23.200
-Where are we going?
-I'll tell you later.

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.870
We have a train to catch.

00:17:24.870 --> 00:17:28.660
But Mayushii hasn't packed,
and we'll need money--

00:17:28.660 --> 00:17:30.750
Don't worry about that.

00:17:30.750 --> 00:17:32.160
Now let's go.

00:17:32.160 --> 00:17:36.040
Oh! Wait, Okarin!

00:17:36.040 --> 00:17:37.580
Umm...!

00:17:37.580 --> 00:17:40.330
-Huh?
-B-Be safe.

00:17:40.330 --> 00:17:43.160
Yeah! See you soon!

00:17:48.830 --> 00:17:52.540
Isn't Akihabara's train station over there?

00:17:52.540 --> 00:17:54.620
We're taking the subway.

00:17:54.620 --> 00:17:56.250
Oh.

00:18:09.330 --> 00:18:16.080
It's been so long since you last
walked with me in tow like this!

00:18:16.080 --> 00:18:17.700
Yeah.

00:18:29.410 --> 00:18:33.160
-Let's turn back.
-Huh?

00:18:51.790 --> 00:18:54.620
All right. Let's go!

00:18:56.540 --> 00:18:58.830
"From: Assistant" "Subject: What happened?"
"You better explain to me later"

00:19:00.250 --> 00:19:02.330
Just Kurisu...

00:19:14.290 --> 00:19:18.540
Huh? Mayushii's watch has stopped...

00:19:18.540 --> 00:19:19.790
That's strange.

00:19:19.790 --> 00:19:23.080
I wound it up just a little while ago...

00:19:26.370 --> 00:19:29.200
It sure is crowded.

00:19:29.200 --> 00:19:31.200
They shut down the Soubu Line.

00:19:31.200 --> 00:19:33.790
Huh? They did?

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:35.370
Yeah.

00:19:35.370 --> 00:19:39.750
Apparently they got a
phone call about a bomb.

00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:41.370
Oh...

00:19:44.500 --> 00:19:47.410
Say, Okarin.

00:19:47.410 --> 00:19:52.580
Umm, Mayushii has lots of things to ask you,

00:19:52.580 --> 00:19:55.120
but she'll hold them in for now, okay?

00:19:56.580 --> 00:20:02.620
Just promise you'll explain
everything when this is over.

00:20:04.500 --> 00:20:06.330
Yeah.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:09.830
I promise.

00:20:12.200 --> 00:20:15.120
-I'm sorry.
-Huh?

00:20:15.120 --> 00:20:20.040
I'm sorry I'm not very useful to you.

00:20:25.830 --> 00:20:29.330
Let's hold that party someday.

00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:31.660
Yeah.

00:20:31.660 --> 00:20:33.290
Someday.

00:20:38.790 --> 00:20:40.410
Someday...

00:20:41.120 --> 00:20:43.040
...for sure.

00:20:47.290 --> 00:20:49.700
Big Sis Mayuri!

00:21:35.830 --> 00:21:37.660
...mean to...

00:21:39.080 --> 00:21:40.950
I didn't mean to...

00:21:42.790 --> 00:21:48.620
All I wanted was to surprise her...

00:21:57.580 --> 00:22:00.200
I won't let her be killed...

00:22:00.200 --> 00:22:05.120
I will save Mayuri...

00:22:05.120 --> 00:22:06.790
I will!

00:22:20.790 --> 00:22:23.870
With my vision restricted,

00:22:23.870 --> 00:22:29.660
there's no escape

00:22:29.660 --> 00:22:32.700
from the merciless control

00:22:32.700 --> 00:22:37.500
of the twelve

00:22:37.500 --> 00:22:41.330
Wishing for

00:22:41.330 --> 00:22:46.370
a tomorrow of repose,

00:22:46.370 --> 00:22:50.450
I embark for the horizon

00:22:50.450 --> 00:22:55.000
of the sacred phenomenon in my hand

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:59.160
Trapped by the covenant

00:22:59.160 --> 00:23:03.540
and shown the outline of false evidence

00:23:03.540 --> 00:23:07.790
the heaven and earth

00:23:07.790 --> 00:23:12.750
of life lets time blindly flow by

00:23:12.750 --> 00:23:18.080
Flutter, butterfly, oh, miraculous butterfly!

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:21.620
I give myself to you

00:23:21.620 --> 00:23:25.870
Oh, butterfly of tears, dazzling butterfly!

00:23:25.870 --> 00:23:28.830
It's all...

00:23:28.830 --> 00:23:33.830
...about to be rewritten now

